<br>
I led a small, multi group raid on PoD today that many of you were at, and we used the new raid interface.  It is VERY sweet, and while EXP was not great spread around that far, I think we had a lot of fun working as a raid and I took home around 4 percent exp gain into 56 by the end.<br>
<br>
The interface makes it very nice, and in options you can color code classes and such, and doubel click names to target etc, makes buffing very easy.<br>
<br>
One nice addition might be the ability to add extra labels other then raid and group leader, such as Main Tank, Secondary Tank, Haster, Slower, Crack etc etc.  This of course isn't neccesary, but it would be cool to be able to type custom labels ;-) <p><table width=100% cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0>
